165
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was because of him!</i></font>

166
00:09:15,780 --> 00:09:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't think you've won yet.</font>

167
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still just a coward who 
ran away and came crawling back!</font>

168
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll hit you with the ultimate Sever, 
infused with my remaining spirit power!</font>

169
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. I ran away.</font>

170
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But running wasn't the end.</font>

171
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not you.</font>

172
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm <i>me</i>.</font>

173
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The past I wanted to erase...</font>

174
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've taken it all on...</font>

175
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be the man I am now!</font>

176
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asshole, asshole, asshole, 
asshole, asshole, asshole!</font>

177
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a flamebaiter like me? 
I don't think so.</font>

178
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me show you what makes us different.</font>

179
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only do I lose your hatred, 
but I also lose to you?</font>

180
00:10:15,430 --> 00:10:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm gonna lose Minoru's love, too!</font>

181
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't bear it!</font>

182
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flames Falling from Heaven!</font>

183
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as I thought.</font>

184
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't run.</font>

185
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I can't forget my desire 
to do things right.</font>

186
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beg pardon.</font>

187
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't mean to use such vulgar language.</font>

188
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="24"><font color="#f4f3f2">Minoru Wagari</font></font></b></font></font>

189
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="24"><font color="#0c0c0b">Out of the fight</font></font></b></font></font>

190
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:56,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I assume you're all done now?</font>

191
00:10:58,490 --> 00:11:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, if I kill you, we lose.</font>

192
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done!</font>

193
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't have any fun with me, 
and Minoru's gonna abandon me.</font>

194
00:11:09,730 --> 00:11:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna die!</font>

195
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Whatever. You brought this 
on yourself, you know?!</font>

196
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just apologize for burning 
Akari's hairpin already!</font>

197
00:11:19,990 --> 00:11:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'm sorry.</font>

198
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I dunno what to do with this guy.</font>

199
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess I'll forgive you.</font>

200
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

201
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time you make fun of 1-B, 
I'm murdering your ass.</font>

202
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="24"><font color="#f4f3f2">Dei Surugi
 <font face="Arial"><b><font size="24"><font color="#0c0c0b">Out of the Fight</font></font></b></font></font></font></b></font></font>

203
00:11:44,490 --> 00:11:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wagari and Surugi both...</font>

204
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can this be?</font>

205
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:52,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soji Enishiro...</font>

206
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soji Enishiro, eh?</font>

207
00:11:57,610 --> 00:12:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ghost account signal was 
detected near here, right?</font>

208
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The signal's getting stronger!</font>

209
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this all about?</font>

210
00:12:06,430 --> 00:12:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's check it out immediately.</font>

211
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I...</font>

212
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please. That was like a toothpick 
compared to what Wagari did.</font>

213
00:12:22,210 --> 00:12:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit sulking already.</font>

214
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you hadn't gotten us away 
with your windows,</font>

215
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we might have all been 
out of the fight by this point.</font>

216
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukuru...</font>

217
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

218
00:12:35,230 --> 00:12:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enishiro?</font>

219
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kasubata, you're all messed up!</font>

220
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up.</font>

221
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to be thriving, though.</font>

222
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

223
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made that Surugi bastard 
apologize for mocking 1-B.</font>

224
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dominated Surugi! Amazing!</font>

225
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys did great yourselves.</font>

226
00:12:57,750 --> 00:13:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at the beating you laid 
on that Wagari guy!</font>

227
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it was a tie.</font>

228
00:13:03,090 --> 00:13:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukuru and I are both down for the count.</font>

229
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next to no battery left.</font>

230
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah.</font>

231
00:13:09,570 --> 00:13:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won!</font>

232
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enishiro.</font>

233
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

234
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, c'mon, it's just the truth, man.</font>

235
00:13:23,070 --> 00:13:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that.</font>

236
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tell you the rest later,</font>

237
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you're the one who opened the window 
he kept shut from me for so long.</font>

238
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes me so happy.</font>

239
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little jealous, really.</font>

240
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the fighters out now are...</font>

241
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#000000">B</font></b></font></font>

242
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#000000">A</font></b></font></font>

243
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#030307">Kasubata\h\h\h\h\h\h\hHasumi\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hUrusugawa</font></font></font>

244
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#030307">Wagari</font></font></font></font>

245
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#030307">Surugi</font></font></font></font>

246
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#030307">Namekawa</font></font></font></font>

247
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#030307">Kusaba</font></font></font></font>

248
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#030307">Owada</font></font></font></font>

249
00:13:39,770 --> 00:13:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three from 1-B and five from 1-A.</font>

250
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means...</font>

251
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only one of them left! Ban Ashina!</font>

252
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this Ashina guy like, anyway?</font>

253
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He thinks of himself 
as a living work of art</font>

254
00:13:59,790 --> 00:14:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and uploads tons of selfies 
to social media.</font>

255
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a responsibility to share 
my beauty with all of humanity!</font>

256
00:14:08,060 --> 00:14:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No part of my body deserves to be hidden!</font>

257
00:14:11,460 --> 00:14:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My beloved followers, look at all of me!</font>

258
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naturally, his account has been frozen 
by mods time and time again.</font>

259
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has freezer-type cyberkinesis.</font>

260
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's extremely stupid...</font>

261
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's powerful.</font>

262
00:14:28,500 --> 00:14:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyber out.</font>

263
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Millennium Suspension.</font>

264
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Title: "Chain of Beautiful Ice."</font>

265
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><b>{\an3}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#100f1b">Chain of
Beautiful <font color="#255ac7">Ice</font></font></font></b></font></font>

266
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyber out.</font>

267
00:14:55,250 --> 00:14:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Millennium Suspension.</font>

268
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Title: "Curtain of Beautiful Ice."</font>

269
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><b>{\an9}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#100f1b">Curtain of Beautiful <font color="#255ac7">Ice</font></font></font></b></font></font>

270
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even ghost accounts 
can be elevated to art!</font>

271
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My cyberkinesis is a beautiful thing!</font>

272
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A freezer, huh?</font>

273
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flames and ice... A hot-and-cold battle.</font>

274
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He probably burned a lot of 
spirit power on that initial ice sculpture.</font>

275
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still there, too.</font>

276
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be no match for you now.</font>

277
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enishiro.</font>

278
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rest is up to you.</font>

279
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! You guys get healed up 
and prepare for the afterparty!</font>

280
00:15:45,090 --> 00:15:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like I'm the last one left.</font>

281
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will make me even more beautiful!</font>

282
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behold my face, tinged with sorrow!</font>

283
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The perfect aesthetic born of solitude!</font>

284
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must share this with my followers!</font>

285
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#fbf4f1">Post</font></b></font></font>

286
00:16:09,420 --> 00:16:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I post this, my account 
will be frozen again.</font>

287
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How unreasonable! 
Is it truly a sin to be so beautiful?!</font>

288
00:16:18,330 --> 00:16:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman">{\an8}<b><font color="#465150">Aid Room</font></b></font></font>

289
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All done!</font>

290
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're totally winning this one.</font>

291
00:16:25,700 --> 00:16:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be so sure.</font>

292
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true that we're 
at a disadvantage right now.</font>

293
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:33,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Ashina-kun can take it!</font>

294
00:16:33,010 --> 00:16:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's got impressive cyberkinesis.</font>

295
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though he is pretty stupid.</font>

296
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashina is a real great guy!</font>

297
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He makes shaved ice for me.</font>

298
00:16:43,670 --> 00:16:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though he is very stupid.</font>

299
00:16:46,020 --> 00:16:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could see that dummy's ice 
send Enishiro's blood flying...</font>

300
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Enishiro's every bit 
as stupid as he is!</font>

301
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that's what you're arguing about?</font>

302
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kochi-sensei, please!</font>

303
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You kids get banged up too often!</font>

304
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The A-B Battle... is coming to an end.</i></font>

305
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Azaki-sensei...</i></font>

306
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:15,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Master...</i></font>

307
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Emoto...</i></font>

308
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:19,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Urusugawa...</i></font>

309
00:17:20,560 --> 00:17:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hasumi...</i></font>

310
00:17:22,470 --> 00:17:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kasubata...</i></font>

311
00:17:23,940 --> 00:17:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They all got me this far!</i></font>

312
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

313
00:17:29,490 --> 00:17:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My precious class 1-A... Damn it!</font>

314
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we've reached the endgame.</font>

315
00:17:34,460 --> 00:17:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's watch until the end, Nanzo-sensei.</font>

316
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't accept this!</font>

317
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you forgotten, Azaki-san?!</font>

318
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How my brother and all those students 
were scorched by K's demon flame?!</font>

319
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I forget?</font>

320
00:17:49,950 --> 00:17:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was my best friend.</font>

321
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Enishiro-kun isn't K.</font>

322
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that, Nanzo-kun.</font>

323
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a report.</font>

324
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The formerly faint ghost account 
readings are rapidly increasing.</font>

325
00:18:11,540 --> 00:18:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a ghost account 
in the fake Kusatsu.</font>

326
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the staff monks on the scene?</font>

327
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't they investigating?</font>

328
00:18:18,300 --> 00:18:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've... lost contact with them.</font>

329
00:18:29,390 --> 00:18:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashina! You're the last member 
standing of class 1-A.</font>

330
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's do this!</font>

331
00:18:36,490 --> 00:18:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

332
00:18:38,390 --> 00:18:41,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just finished it.</font>

333
00:18:41,910 --> 00:18:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Title:</font>

334
00:18:44,170 --> 00:18:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The Frozen Weak"!</font>

335
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The staff monks?!</font>

336
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're... dead?</font>

337
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As their creator, I regret to say...</font>

338
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no good.</font>

339
00:18:59,710 --> 00:19:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not up to my standards.</font>

340
00:19:02,470 --> 00:19:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do?!</font>

341
00:19:04,150 --> 00:19:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't do the A-B Battle like—</font>

342
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

343
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just getting started.</font>

344
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sick of things.</font>

345
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't be suspended anymore!</font>

346
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tears of blood!</i></font>

347
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've wanted this for so long...</font>

348
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An account that couldn't be frozen.</font>

349
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A body that wouldn't age or die.</font>

350
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And wings!</font>

351
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Ashina?</font>

352
00:19:40,490 --> 00:19:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what we picked up?</font>

353
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's already dead.</font>

354
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a ghost account!</font>

355
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Title:</font>

356
00:19:55,510 --> 00:19:59,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#100f1b">{\an7}Re<font color="#255ac7">birth <font color="#000000">in Bestial Beauty</font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

357
00:19:55,530 --> 00:19:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Rebirth in Bestial Beauty"!</font>

358
00:19:55,630 --> 00:19:59,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="14"><font color="#454744">Ban Ashina</font></font></font></font>

359
00:20:00,050 --> 00:20:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A ghost account?</font>

360
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And tears of blood?</font>

361
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me...</font>

362
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at my incredible body!</font>

363
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can even do this!</font>

364
00:20:11,450 --> 00:20:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Title:</font>

365
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#100f1b">The Great Hot Springs <font color="#255ac7">Town <font color="#000000">Freeze</font></font></font></font></b></font>

366
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}"The Great Hot Springs Town Freeze!"</font>

367
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:22,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a beautiful sight!</font>

368
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much, K.</font>

369
00:20:24,990 --> 00:20:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sad Boy K...</font>

370
00:20:27,210 --> 00:20:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had him turn you into a ghost account?</font>

371
00:20:30,970 --> 00:20:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What now? A blizzard?!</font>

372
00:20:33,710 --> 00:20:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's cold!</font>

373
00:20:35,130 --> 00:20:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a barrier.</font>

374
00:20:36,840 --> 00:20:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's covering all of the fake Kusatsu.</font>

375
00:20:39,890 --> 00:20:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can enter... or leave.</font>

376
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashina-kun...</font>

377
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What do I do?</font>

378
00:20:56,940 --> 00:21:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master K, you seem quite pleased.</font>

379
00:21:00,580 --> 00:21:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, the thought of my dream 
coming true makes me happy.</font>

380
00:21:05,450 --> 00:21:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master K, seeing you so happy...</font>

381
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:14,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes me happy, too!</font>

382
00:21:14,910 --> 00:21:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He really is special to you, isn't he?</font>

383
00:21:20,150 --> 00:21:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could this happen?!</font>

384
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashina... A student of
 1-A has been killed?!</font>

385
00:21:25,570 --> 00:21:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K turned him into a ghost account?!</font>

386
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Nanzo-kun.</font>

387
00:21:31,340 --> 00:21:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wanted this for himself.</font>

388
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Azaki-sensei.</i></font>

389
00:21:37,470 --> 00:21:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't enter the fake Kusatsu.</font>

390
00:21:39,740 --> 00:21:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an extremely powerful barrier.</font>

391
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think he's a mid-level ghost account...</font>

392
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, high-level!</font>

393
00:21:49,210 --> 00:21:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ban Ashina...</font>

394
00:21:51,230 --> 00:21:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you were stupid, but I didn't 
think you were <i>this</i> stupid.</font>

395
00:21:55,890 --> 00:21:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soji Enishiro...</font>

396
00:21:57,610 --> 00:22:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you and make you 
an artistic offering to K!</font>

397
00:22:02,090 --> 00:22:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll exorcise you here and now!</font>

